  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThe current TreeHash implementation for structs (containers) does not use merkle_hash as per the [spec](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/dev/specs/simple-serialize.md#container-2).\r\n\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\nFields within a container are TreeHashed, concatenated, and hashed.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\nFields within a container should be TreeHashed, added to a list which is then merklized.\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nCorrect the algorithm which is implemented in the TreeHash macro.",
